Scientists do not join hands every Saturday or Sunday and sing, "Yes,
gravity is real! I know gravity is real! I will have faith! I will be
strong! I believe in my heart that what goes up, up, up must come down,
down, down. Amen!" If they did, we would think they were pretty insecure
about the concept.
    --Dan Barker, _Godless_ (p.101)
